'use strict';

module.exports = {
    COMPARISON_OPS: ['=', '!=', '<', '>=', '>', '<='],
    COMPARISON_OPS2: ['=', '<', '>=', '>', '<='],

    SET_OPS: ['{}', '}{'],
    CONSTRAINT_REDUCTION: {
        // for contour constraints, open/closed endpoints are equivalent
        '=': '=',

        '<': '<',

        '>': '>',

        '[]': '[]',
        '()': '[]',
        '[)': '[]',

        '][': '][',
        ')(': '][',
